99
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:20,760
<i>You have not reached</i>
<i>your target destination.</i>

100
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:23,040
<i>Records indicate you are the first human</i>

101
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:25,280
<i>to reach this unexplored planet</i>
<i>or asteroid.</i>

102
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:28,280
<i>You are legally entitled to name it.</i>
<i>Please enter now.</i>

103
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:29,800
- No.
<i>- Searching.</i>

104
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,600
<i>The name "No" is already in use.</i>

105
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:33,280
- No. Not "No."
<i>- Searching.</i>

106
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:35,400
<i>The name "No Not No"</i>
<i>is already in use.</i>

107
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,480
Fuck off, LEONARD.

108
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:40,080
<i>Searching. The name</i>
<i>"Fuck Off Leonard" is available.</i>

109
00:11:40,160 --> 00:11:41,400
<i>Would you like to use it?</i>

110
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:43,160
Yeah, sure. Why not?

111
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,400
<i>Request confirmed.</i>

112
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:47,520
<i>Sending the name to the registry</i>
<i>of extrasolar bodies and planets.</i>

113
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:52,520
